Tango-app REQUIREMENTS
**********************

- a user should be able to access the whole database
  entries
- a user should be able to query the database to find
  events of interest
- a user should be able to login to post events
- a user should be able to access the database even with
  no internet connection (if some data were cached before)
- a user should be able to specify if the update service
  must be started at boot time or only when the application
  is first opened

Fancy features
**************

- new events widget on the home screen
